          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-1" n="1">A<hi rend="small-caps">N</hi> ass's hoof alone can hold</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-2" n="2">That poisonous juice, which kills by cold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-3" n="3">Methought, when I this poem read,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-4" n="4">No vessel but an ass's head</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-5" n="5">Such frigid fustian could contain;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-6" n="6">I mean, the head without the brain.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-7" n="7">The cold conceits, the chilling thoughts,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-8" n="8">Went down like stupifying draughts;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-9" n="9">I found my head begin to swim,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-10" n="10">A numbness crept through every limb.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-11" n="11">In haste, with imprecations dire,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-12" n="12">I threw the volume in the fire;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-13" n="13">When, (who could think?) though cold as ice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-14" n="14">It burnt to ashes in a trice.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-15" n="15">How could I more enhance its fame?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-469-14W2-line-16" n="16">Though born in snow, it died in flame.</l>
          </lg>
